      p Appbot is build on top of work from the Open Source Community, the best of the best!
      p The architecture is based on a Centralized Api Approach, like the Obama Campaing for America
      p The infrastructure runs on Cloud Computing Champion Amazon Web Services
      h4 Appbot is about being the best of the best
      
