      p Appbot solves the enterprise dilemma by defining a new paradigm for Enterprise Software. 
      p Organizations should build their own software and that software reason to exist should be to be modified.
      h4 Appbot builds the complete infrastructure to handle one to millions of visitors, pay for what you use.
      h4 Appbot help build and guide teams to customise the platform and innovate with software
      h3 Appbot is great!
